ications for governments aiming at improving access to finance to overcome income inequality problems, and also improve their growth.Originality/value: The results provide initial evidence of the aggregate explanatory power of interest rates and financial literacy for the criterion variable, access to formal credit by SMEs. © Emerald Group Publishing Limited.
